class.description:
@brief Animation overlay settings class for the KdsCharacter module.
This class extends the UDataAsset class and includes properties for managing
animation overlays based on gameplay tags.

@brief Base component class for the KdsCharacter module.
This class extends the UActorComponent class and includes additional functionality
for handling character-specific behavior.

@brief Debug component class for the KdsCharacter module.
This class extends the UActorComponent class and includes additional functionality
for handling character-specific debug behavior.

@brief Core character class for the KdsCharacter module.
This class extends the AAlsCharacter class and includes additional functionality
for handling animation overlay settings and overlay mode changes.

@brief Linked animation instance class for the KdsCharacter module.
This class extends the UAlsLinkedAnimationInstance class and includes additional functionality
for handling settings related to linked animation instances.

@brief Linked animation instance settings class for the KdsCharacter module.
This class extends the UDataAsset class and includes properties for managing
settings related to linked animation instances.

@brief Playable character class for the KdsCharacter module.
This class extends the AKds_CoreCharacter class and includes additional functionality
for handling the basic movement, this class also handles the input actions for the character and camera.
